                <note rend="inline" type="source">123M956/387: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Consul General at Algiers (<persName type="to">Cole</persName>)</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-08-01T15:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 1, 1942—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>229. For Robert D. Murphy. You are directed proceed Department for consultation
                    as soon as possible. [Here follow travel orders.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Welles</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
